{
  "stem": "304.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In my train, we didn't have steps, so we jumped down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for the older people, the pregnant women, the sick people, we helped down-- we helped down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we came out of the train, we stood there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I looked right and left, it was like a wall of people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A wall of people standing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is the first picture I saw, the people standing, a wall of people, and the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then we were told-- everybody had those bundles, little-- little, big suitcases-- put your luggage there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they pointed to a place, and we all went to this place to put down our bundles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I came there, I saw that, like, a mountain of luggages, all shapes, sizes, and colors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I put down mine, I said, oh, how will I recognize it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't put my name on it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, I never had this problem, to recognize it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there we are standing, just the clothes on our body, and we went back at the previous position to stand next to the train.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then came the first real order from the Germans and the first separation of families.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Men here and women here!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Schnell, schnell, they shouted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from that moment, until the liberation, every order was given in German, and every time they added a million times the schnell, fast.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They always pushed us, fast, fast, so we wouldn't have time to think or to do something else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, in spite of everything, eventually we learned to do other things than they told us in order to save our lives.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, suddenly, we find ourselves separated from the families.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We still could see each other, and everybody's trying to talk.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
